00:12:20,244 --> 00:12:23,665
Mike just spoke about, but the social side of VR we are true

214
00:12:23,705 --> 00:12:26,965
believers in. There's been certainly a lot of talk at

215
00:12:27,005 --> 00:12:30,866
least early on about how VR is isolating and all of this. Well,

216
00:12:31,026 --> 00:12:33,947
we don't believe that whatsoever. And in fact, we

217
00:12:34,187 --> 00:12:39,568
