218
00:12:39,628 --> 00:12:40,888
approach from the very beginning.

219
00:12:41,408 --> 00:12:46,552
You can almost call it a core mechanic of ours. We've always really been into a shared experience.

220
00:12:47,112 --> 00:12:51,816
Not only do you get these great up close immersive experiences on your own,

221
00:12:52,216 --> 00:12:57,580
but the value of that, the excitement of that is exponentially increased when you can share that with a friend.

222
00:12:58,081 --> 00:13:03,805
So co-op has been really important. You'll see that continue in things that Servios does.

223
00:13:04,946 --> 00:13:09,329
